data.description: Financing available for VA assumable! Ask your Broker for details!  Welcome to the Grand Fir!  This impressive 2602 sq ft Craftsman home delivers all the space you desire!  Incredible features include large inviting entry, office, open concept kitchen, large eat in space, large living room w/gas fireplace. Upper level boasts large bonus room/flex/bedroom, Primary suite w/tray ceilings, ceiling fan, 5/p bath of Primary & WIC.  Utility room located upstairs& 3 additional generous bedrooms!!!  Enjoy large patio out back, and savor privacy on the outer lot.  Fully fenced yard, 3 car garage, sprinkler system for easy landscaping. Home has NEW AC & Water heater!  Conveniently located near shopping,schools,parks,minutes away from 1-5,& JBLM.
